<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Zealot Paladin is a classic fast hitting melee character who can handle a large variety of mobs but lacks in Area of Effect. With a couple of key Items he can take down bosses and single monsters extremely quickly. Overall he is one of the stronger melee characters in the game and can play through PvE quite quickly for a physical Damage build.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Zealot. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Fanaticism@@@ - The main Aura used for this character, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Zeal@@@ - Main Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Sacrifice@@@ - Synergy for @@@D2Zeal@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2HolyShield@@@ - Great for Max Block, required</li>
</ol>

